[0m[49m[39m  17, 18[0m:[39m[49m ## What Works
[0m[49m[39m  18, 19[0m:[39m[49m 
[0m[49m[39m  19, 20[0m:[39m[49m - Pre-exploration step that fetches profile, passwords, and API descriptions before LLM reasoning eliminates wasted steps on API discovery
[0m[49m[39m  20, 21[0m:[39m[49m - Correct API names in system prompt: search_api_docs, show_api_doc, show_api_descriptions
[0m[49m[39m  21, 22[0m:[39m[49m - Explicit auth token pattern: login returns access_token, pass it to every authenticated call
[0m[49m[39m  22, 23[0m:[39m[49m - Pagination guidance: keep incrementing page until empty
[0m[49m[39m  23, 24[0m:[39m[49m - MAX_STEPS=25 gives enough room for complex multi-step tasks
[0m[49m[39m  24, 25[0m:[39m[49m - maxTokens=4096 allows more complete code generation per step
[0m[49m[39m  25, 26[0m:[39m[49m - App detection from instruction keywords to pre-fetch only relevant API docs
[0m[49m[39m  26, 27[0m:[39m[49m - Concise system prompt with 5 EARS-style rules keeps model focused
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     28[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - Explicit answer format rule for numeric values: plain numbers without "$", units, or formatting — fixes float normalization in eval tests
