[0m[49m[39m  36, 38[0m:[39m[49m ## Codebase Notes
[0m[49m[39m  37, 39[0m:[39m[49m 
[0m[49m[39m  38, 40[0m:[39m[49m - `src/agent.py` is the only file to modify — contains SYSTEM_PROMPT, call_llm(), extract_code(), solve_task()
[0m[49m[39m  39, 41[0m:[39m[49m - `src/llm_call.py` reads MODEL_ID from env and calls Bedrock converse API — FORBIDDEN to modify
[0m[49m[39m  40, 42[0m:[39m[49m - `src/run_eval.py` runs tasks sequentially or in parallel with ProcessPoolExecutor — FORBIDDEN to modify
[0m[49m[39m  41, 43[0m:[39m[49m - The agent's call_llm() auto-prefixes "us." to MODEL_ID if needed for cross-region inference
[0m[49m[39m  42, 44[0m:[39m[49m - world.execute(code) runs Python code in AppWorld sandbox (stdlib + pendulum only)
[0m[49m[39m  43, 45[0m:[39m[49m - world.task_completed() checks if complete_task() was called
[0m[49m[39m  44, 46[0m:[39m[49m - Pre-exploration runs world.execute() calls before the LLM loop — these don't count against MAX_STEPS but do affect the sandbox state
[0m[49m[39m  45, 47[0m:[39m[49m - App keyword detection: spotify (song/playlist/album/artist/music/play/listen/genre/track), venmo (payment/transaction/money), phone (text/message/call/alarm/spam), simple_note (note/bucket list), splitwise (bill/expense/split/roommate/coworker/friend/sibling), file_system (file/csv/export/photo/compress/zip/directory/~/), amazon (order/product)
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     48[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - Eval tests for monetary answers use `normalize=float` with `tolerance=0.51` — answers must be parseable as Python float
